[SHORT DESC]
Effects vary with terrain.

[LONG DESC]
<p>Effects vary with terrain. Has a 30% chance to have the given effect associated with each terrain on the target. Link battles are counted as Building.</p>

<dl>
<dt>Building/Link/Other</dt>
<dd>Paralyzes</dd>
<dt>Tall Grass</dt>
<dd>Poison</dd>
<dt>Very tall grass</dt>
<dd>Sleep</dd>
<dt>Sand</dt>
<dd>Lowers Accuracy 1 stage</dd>
<dt>Cave</dt>
<dd>Flinches</dd>
<dt>Rocky surface</dt>
<dd>Confuses</dd>
<dt>Pond</dt>
<dd>Lowers Speed 1 stage</dd>
<dt>Sea</dt>
<dd>Lowers Attack 1 stage</dd>
</dl>